Subject: [PATCH 16/31] resort: serve calabogie as trails instead of lifts

The page has no per-lift data - the rows smuggled into the lifts slot
were trails. Move them to the trails plugin with difficulty levels from
the section headers, and disable the lifts plugin for this resort.
